AUDIO: 'distinct voice, and that its personality and skills unlock over time through interaction. &gt;&gt; Shabbat, [music] shabbat. &gt;&gt; Me? &gt;&gt; Mama, mama, mama. &gt;&gt; Because the AI processes these interactions locally, [music] your'

